item.title: A conversation with YÜTH MAGAZINE_Carson Kropfl and Mikey Walshe
item.description: This week, we’re stoked to welcome two longtime friends who grew up in the surf town of San Clemente. Frustrated with the state of social media and feeling like their generation was missing a true print publication that represented their lifestyle — surf, skate, snow, music, art, and everything in between. These college visionaries took matters into their own hands... Feed: https://anchor.fm/s/103f7e9d8/podcast/rss
